{"tid":2382532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特首林鄭月娥：已物色幾個　指定（限制）區域　將「突襲式」進行","createTime":"2021-01-27T10:37:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T12:20:28.000Z","uid":261647,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"2c228594711b60d8f1374d182d21319f5e1f856a","tid":2382532,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T10:37:05.000Z","msg":"https://news. rthk. hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572405-20210126.htm<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hRaFeez.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhRaFeez.png&h=6fd1daaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥總結在佐敦設立「受限區域」的行動，形容整體順暢有成效，做到以人為本。在後續執法行動中，找到200多名無按要求進行檢測的居民，資料已交衞生防護中心跟進。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥指出，保密工作方面有需要改善，將來會更聚焦及縮小受限區域範圍，並會壓縮限制市民離開的時間。<br />\n<br />\n她又說，將來在檢測方面會做得更進取，形容要「走在社區爆發前」，當局亦已物色多幾個指定區域，稍後會公布。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林鄭話會「突襲式」封樓:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2380485/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2380485/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"3f6f6f3dac532f694b83c9497a7c5c79f4514750","tid":2382532,"uid":208323,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T10:37:52.000Z","msg":"佢仲覺得自己唔夠痴線"},{"pid":"9027859814d33c67b9a8c453719e72ca51482d60","tid":2382532,"uid":154373,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T10:38:33.000Z","msg":"日日殘民撚民爽能到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BeG5rfM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBeG5rfM.png&h=e9b32541&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cdd22032ef38983c95329089917403059aef908b","tid":2382532,"uid":291750,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T10:38:38.000Z","msg":"今個weekend要盡量四圍行先得。"},{"pid":"bc96978c604f1c2d3ea17d51347a0a981ea429e8","tid":2382532,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T10:58:00.000Z","msg":"玩封區玩上癮<img src=\"/assets/face